user: Where would you recommend me to take a kidney transplant surgery?
system: Addenbrooke's Hospital has a Transplant High Dependency Unit which cares for patients who are undergoing liver, kidney, pancreas, and multi-organ transplantation. You may contact the hospital for further inquiries. 
user: But I am worried that the surgery might be painful and dreadful. 
system: Please visit the hospital if you feel sick. It is better to administer treatment early. 